# MONEY::NETWORK_CASINO_SELL_CHIPS

## Summary
Maybe add cash - remove chips. can be called with amount 0. chips will be changed on consoles and value must > 0

## Parameters
* **INT** amount
* **INT** chips

## Returns
* **BOOL**
